import React from 'react';
import {Navbar} from "react-bootstrap";



const Cmheader =() => {

    return (
        <CmHeader>
            <Navbar
                bg="dark"
                variant="dark"
                className="mb-4" >
                <Navbar.Brand href="/">
                    Home
                </Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Brand href="/main">
                    Main
                </Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Brand href="/dashboard">
                    Dashboard
                </Navbar.Brand>
            </Navbar>

        </CmHeader>
    )
}

export default Cmheader
